<section class="reviews-mini">
  <div class="wrap-wide">
    <div class="reviews-mini-head">
      <span class="eyebrow">Real reviews</span>
      <h2>Trusted by <em>athletes</em> across every sport.</h2>
      <div class="reviews-mini-meta">
        <span class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg width="16" height="16"><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</span>
        <strong>4.9 / 5</strong>
        <span>Based on 2,400+ verified reviews</span>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="reviews-mini-grid">
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">🎾 Tennis · 4x / week</span>
        <h5>Cramping just stopped</h5>
        <p>Used to cramp in the third set every match in summer. One IONIQ before warm-up, one between sets. Hasn't happened in three months. My second serve is still there at 5–5.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">SK</span><span><strong>Sarah K.</strong>Verified buyer · Tennis player</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">🏃 Marathon · 60km/wk</span>
        <h5>Long-run recovery is night-and-day</h5>
        <p>Switched off sugar gels mid-block, ran the IONIQ protocol pre and post. Two months in, my recovery between long runs is the best it's been in five years.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">MP</span><span><strong>Mark P.</strong>Verified buyer · Marathon</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">🥎 Padel · 3x / week</span>
        <h5>Sharper in the third set</h5>
        <p>Padel in Dubai heat is brutal — by the third set I'd be sloppy on the glass. One before warm-up, one mid-match. Focus stays sharp until the end.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">JD</span><span><strong>James D.</strong>Verified buyer · Padel player</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">⚽ Football · 5-a-side</span>
        <h5>Replaced four products with one</h5>
        <p>Was carrying electrolyte tabs, a pre-workout, magnesium for sleep, and a vitamin B12 spray. Now it's one sachet pre, one post. Same training load, less stuff.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">ML</span><span><strong>Marco L.</strong>Verified buyer · 5-a-side football</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">🚴 Cycling · 200km / wk</span>
        <h5>Hot-weather riding finally works</h5>
        <p>Used to bonk on summer rides — bottle of sugar drink wasn't cutting it. IONIQ pre, IONIQ during, IONIQ post on big days. Heat doesn't break me the same way anymore.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">AR</span><span><strong>Anna R.</strong>Verified buyer · Cyclist</span></div>
      </div>
      <div class="rev-card">
        <div class="stars">{% for i in (1..5) %}<svg><use href="#i-star"/></svg>{% endfor %}</div>
        <span class="sport-tag">🏋️ CrossFit · 5x / week</span>
        <h5>The mental focus is the unlock</h5>
        <p>Strength gains were already there, but the focus on heavy days under fatigue — that was new. Nootropics actually working at clinical doses.</p>
        <div class="by"><span class="avt">TG</span><span><strong>Tom G.</strong>Verified buyer · CrossFit</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
{% schema %}
{ "name": "Reviews grid", "presets": [{ "name": "Reviews grid" }] }
{% endschema %}